{
  "name": "robinhood-trading-bot",
  "version": "0.2.0",
  "description": "Automated trading bot for Robinhood Chain (chain ID 4663): rule-based entries on new launchpad pairs (NOXA + The Odyssey) with full on-chain data (holders, dev buy, liquidity, curve flow), plus copy trading that mirrors tracked wallets. Web dashboard, CLI, optional Telegram alerts. Paper mode by default.",
